        "Description": "Before his time, Ritter, &quot;The Sparrow&quot;, discovered that some of his hires, bribed by one of his yacht members, Nathan Melendez, were working overtime to gather evidence on his life of theft.\r\rNot just fearful, he was furious, and comissioned ICA for specifically painful hits on each of them, with care not to harm any others.\r\rTo help with discretion, he arranged their routines to be more isolated, had Nathan cornered into a bathroom by security and tucked an arsenal outside.\r\rAlso try suit only!",
